{
  "page": "Feature quote/259",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“<a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Your father</a> is called the Mad King in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>. Has no one ever told you?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a><br />“<a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys</a> did. <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">The Usurper</a> called him that, the Usurper and <a href=\"/index.php/Usurper%27s_dogs\" title=\"Usurper&#39;s dogs\">his dogs</a>.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a><br />“Why ask for truth, if you close your ears to it?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_71\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 71\">Chapter 71</a>, Daenerys VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404134428\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.013 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 122/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 312/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser f